Class BasicGraph

  • public class BasicGraph
extends ImportedGraph
    A class that allows for importing and exporting of any type of graph, using build in JUNG export/import functionality NOTE: The edges of this graph will not match, since vertex and edge ids will not be the same. The value of the vertex and edges will though
